title: SMALL GROUP TRAINING
description: Our Small Group Personal Training is unlike anything you'll have experienced before. In micro training groups of just 6:1, all your workouts are customised, recorded and coached by an experienced personal trainer.

description: 1-2-1 personal training is the ultimate investment in your health. You'll be working directly with your coach in our private studio, following a bespoke plan to ensure you hit your goals in record time.

title: NUTRITION COACHING
description: We'll teach you how to take control of your health and weight, without relying on any specific diet or products, with our 1-2-1 nutrition coaching.

title: ONLINE TRAINING
description: The Titan's Online Coaching Packages have been created to take the guesswork out of getting in the best shape of your life.

title: MAYFAIR PHYSIOTHERAPY
description: Physiotherapy at Titan Fitness Club is offered by MAYFAIR PHYSIOTHERAPY. The team of fully qualified, chartered Physiotherapists continue to be an integral part of our clubs and play an important role in the fitness journey of our clients
